INSERT INTO Question (id,realmId,type,text,regDate,updateDate) OVERRIDING SYSTEM VALUE VALUES (339,4,1,'Какие строки из нижеприведенного примера НЕ скомпилируются?<br /><br />14: private static int one;<br />15: private static final int two;<br />16: private static final int three = 3;<br />17: private static final int four;<br />18: static {<br />19:&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; one = 1;<br />20:&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; two = 2;<br />21:&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; three = 3;<br />22:&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; two = 4;<br />23: }',TIMESTAMP '1970-01-01 03:00:00',TIMESTAMP '1970-01-01 03:00:00');
